parameters: SetCharLight 0 2 1 15
Hey, Akane. Wake up.
00_st_akane01_smile

Akane: Ah, Reisha, huh. Thanks for your hard work as always.
You finished with the guys early today, did you get better
at making them cum?
00_st_akane01_nomal
Akane: ...Huh? You're alone? Where's the guard?
00_st_akane01_serious
Akane: Hey! What's this!?

Don't raise your voice. If you make too much noise, they'll
come.
00_st_akane01_serious
Akane: S-sorry... But, this thing you have...!

Is this the tool you asked me to bring for you? Is it
correct?
00_st_akane01_smile
Akane: Yeah, that's right! It's my lockpicking tool!

Good. Then let's get to it right away. I have a favor to ask
of you.
00_st_akane01_smile

Akane: Sure. There's no reason for me to refuse here. Let's
hear it.

We don't have much time. First, open this door and get out
of here. I'll explain the details while you work.
00_st_akane01_serious
Akane: You can't mean...!
Yes. We're getting out of this place, to the outside.
00_st_akane01_nomal

Akane: How did you manage to get out? Aren't you supposed to
be with the boss at this time?
00_st_akane01_serious
Akane: Don't tell me... you killed him...?

Don't be stupid. He's a detestable man, but I didn't take
his life.

I've been observing his behavior for the past few days. He's
a simple man. His actions after being serviced are
predictable.

I waited until he let his guard down and started snoring
after he thought he had tamed me. He probably won't be able
to get up from his bed for a few days.

I had planned to escape as soon as my wounds healed and I
understood the situation I was in. It seems like the right
time now.

(Although, I should keep to myself that it would have been
impossible without finding someone to unlock the door. It's
not that I don't trust her, but there's no need to owe her
more than necessary...)

There was an unexpected delay, but now that I know they have
no intention of keeping their promises, there's no need to
play along anymore.

(...And if we hurry with the escape, maybe there's still
time...)

I've come to realize once again that what those in charge
here are doing is unforgivable. There is no one here to
condemn the evil deeds done in the shadows.

That's why they must be judged under the law. To prevent any
more victims.
00_st_akane01_serious

Akane: You're moving ahead on your own here, but you know
there are many who came here on their own because they
couldn't exist under the sun anymore.

Akane: If we do this, we might be taking away the only place
these shady people have. Do you understand what you're
saying?

Akane: And about being judged under the law, you seem to
trust this country quite a bit. But I really doubt that the
judicial folks will listen to us about what happens here...

No problem there. Once I return to the castle and explain
everything, they will act immediately.
00_st_akane01_nomal

Akane: Huh? What are you talking about? The castle, as in
the royal capital? They won't listen to people of our
status.

I can't expect you to believe me looking like this, but I
serve at the castle. I'm currently away on a certain duty,
but within the royal capital, no one would doubt my word.
00_st_akane01_anger
Akane: Ahh, no use talking to this one. She doesn't get it.

I can provide a place for women and children, and others who
have lost their way, though it may not be very spacious, on
my own lands.

Of course, those who should be judged will have to face
their crimes to some extent.
00_st_akane01_anger

Akane: Hmm, what should I do? I'm starting to worry about
lending a hand.

Hmph, say whatever you want. But you're going to help with
the escape. Without you, we won't succeed in getting out of
here.

That is, of course, if "your skills are as good as you
claim."
00_st_akane01_smile

Akane: What? You're surprisingly good at firing people
up...! Hehehe♪
00_st_akane01_smile

Akane: Well alright then. You listened to my request before.
Now it's only fair that I listen to yours!
Akane: Let's do it! Let's go outside!
